OL,3,CIs Badenoch right to propose the end
OL,4,Cof stamp duty?
OL,6,FStamp duty is a terrible tax. It is
OL,7,Fnot a tax on bad actions and
OL,8,Fbehaviour, the kind of tax that may
OL,9,Fhave a legitimate social purpose, like
OL,10,Fthe duty on cigarettes. It actually
OL,11,Fdiscourages activity that would be
OL,12,Fgood for the economy and good for
OL,13,Fsociety.
OL,15,FThe duty dampens the market for
OL,16,Fhouses. It discourages people from
OL,17,Fselling and buying homes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
