OL,3,CIs Badenoch right to propose the end
OL,4,Cof stamp duty?
OL,6,FAs such, it means older people stay in
OL,7,Fhomes that have become far too big for
OL,8,Fthem. It keeps house prices out of
OL,9,Freach for young people. And it creates
OL,10,Fa disincentive for people to look far
OL,11,Fand wide for a new job, because of the
OL,12,Fincremental cost of selling up and
OL,13,Fbuying a new property.
OL,15,FSo, for all the #8bn to #9bn giveaways
OL,16,FKemi Badenoch could have dangled to
OL,17,Fshore up her and her party's flagging
OL,18,Fsupport, and for all your inevitable
OL,19,Fcynicism that this is a naked bribe,
OL,20,Fthere are many worse stunts she could
OL,21,Fhave pulled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
