OL,3,CIs Badenoch right to propose the end
OL,4,Cof stamp duty?
OL,6,FAs it happens, the Chancellor Rachel
OL,7,FReeves and the Treasury have been
OL,8,Flooking at doing the same, though as
OL,9,Fpart of a wider reform of taxation on
OL,10,Fhousing, which would involve the
OL,11,Fimposition of a new annual tax on the
OL,12,Fvalue of more expensive properties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
